Arsene Wenger on his time at Arsenal: &quot;&ldquo;I&rsquo;m proud. At the end of the day when you look back you don&rsquo;t think about what you won and what you lost so much, but I&rsquo;m proud for having the attitude just to serve the club as long as I was there.&quot;<br />
<br />
Wenger: &quot;I have more satisfaction today when I look back and I see the Emirates, we built all that without a penny from anybody and today the club can take off even more and be more successful.&rdquo;
